Package de.rwth_aachen.swc.eaqtool.view

Class ViewOutput

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth_aachen.swc.eaqtool.view.ViewOutput
  • public class ViewOutput
extends java.lang.Object
    Dumb and simple output object to be sent to a view for display (a more elaborated view might need something more elaborated ;-)) header: Map of Strings to be displayed as a header section, K=name/description, V=content data: Map of K=category Id (eg. QRC), V=Map of K=Data provider name, V=list of data Strings (norm. value, raw value, BL-marker) bltotals: Map of K=category Id, V=Map of V=BL, K=% of occurences in this category qindex: Map of K=BL, K=overall % of occurences
